{"title":"Selle San Marco Mantra Saddle for Gravel, Trail, or Enduro","link":"https://theradavist.com/selle-san-marco-mantra-saddle/","date":1728582886000,"content":"<p><em>Selle San Marco expands its gravel and off-road cycling collection with the new <a href=\"https://sellesanmarco.com/search.php?search_query=mantra\" target=\"_blank\">Mantra</a> saddle, designed specifically for enduro, trail and gravel riders. Though minimalist in appearance, the Mantra is packed with technical features.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra2.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>With the new Mantra, Selle San Marco redefines its approach to off-road cycling. The streamlined, clean design allows for advanced technical solutions developed by Selle San Marco, headquartered in Asolo, to ensure optimal movement control and proper positioning while riding.</p>\n<p>The standout feature of the Mantra is its delta shape, which helps riders easily find the correct and most functional position on the saddle – crucial on rough terrain where constant vibrations and frequent shifts in posture are the norm. Additionally, the saddle’s completely flat profile allows for greater freedom of movement.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?resize=1200,1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra7.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?resize=1200,1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra6.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?resize=1200,1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra3.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The wide, padded nose (&gt;40mm) provides enhanced comfort during climbs and better control during descents, while the open body design reduces pressure on the perineal area. The saddle cover is sealed, however, to keep mud from passing through the hole.</p>\n<p>Available in the idmatch L2 size, with rails in three versions: Carbon FX, Xsilite and Manganese.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?resize=1200,1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra5.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra4.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Selle-San-Marco-Mantra4.jpg?resize=1200,1200&amp;quali